& [RunLocalOutputReviewDesign] is the design contract for reviewing generated run-local outputs before merge or apply eligibility
  @ [run_local_execution_design] coordination/gate_authorized_run_local_execution_design.sop
  @ [manual_merge_policy] coordination/manual_merge_packet_policy.sop
  @ [apply_policy] coordination/operator_approved_apply_policy.sop
  @ [manager_job_notice] coordination/manager_job_notice.sop
  @ [created_at] 2026-05-29T23:56:00Z

  + [design_status] is ready_for_implementation_slice
  + [authority_boundary] is run_local_output_review_design_not_merge_or_apply_acceptance
  + [primary_goal] is require Manager and Shaliach review evidence over run-local generated outputs before they can be considered for merge packet construction
  + [non_goal] is target workspace mutation
  + [non_goal] is manual merge packet generation
  + [non_goal] is apply or rollback approval
  + [non_goal] is Manager frontier advancement

& [ReviewInputs] is the evidence reviewers must inspect
  + [required_ref] is RunLocalExecutionPlan
  + [required_ref] is RunLocalExecutionResult
  + [required_ref] is generated file refs under the plan run-local root
  + [required_ref] is WorkerCycleRecord for execution outcome
  + [required_ref] is proof result cycle when proof was run
  + [required_ref] is active conversation current_frontier
  + [authority_boundary] is review_inputs_not_patch_acceptance
  = must: reject generated file refs outside the run-local worker execution root
  = must: preserve generated file refs as evidence, not target workspace paths

& [ManagerRunLocalOutputReview] is the Manager-side review artifact
  + [artifact_name] is runs/<run_id>/worker_execution/<cycle_id>/manager_run_local_output_review.sop
  + [review_status] is accepted_for_merge_review, rejected, needs_revision, or needs_human_review
  + [plan_ref] is required
  + [result_ref] is required
  + [generated_file_set] is required
  + [frontier_at_review] is required
  + [risk_summary] is required
  + [authority_boundary] is manager_run_local_review_not_apply_acceptance
  = must: never mark target workspace files accepted
  = must: require separate manual merge packet before any target workspace apply

& [ShaliachRunLocalOutputReview] is the protocol counsel review artifact
  + [artifact_name] is runs/<run_id>/worker_execution/<cycle_id>/shaliach_run_local_output_review.sop
  + [review_status] is clear, warning, rework_required, pause_required, or needs_human_review
  + [plan_ref] is required
  + [result_ref] is required
  + [checked_protocol_set] is SOP, SJS, DataDrivenDesign, lineage, uncertainty, artifact_form, and workspace_boundary
  + [finding_summary] is required
  + [required_response] is proceed_to_merge_review, revise_run_local_output, pause_for_manager, or human_review
  + [authority_boundary] is shaliach_run_local_review_not_manager_acceptance
  = must: pause when generated refs escape the run-local root
  = must: request rework when SJS or DataDesign support is thin for generated behavior changes

& [MergeEligibilitySummary] is the non-mutating combined review result
  + [artifact_name] is runs/<run_id>/worker_execution/<cycle_id>/run_local_merge_eligibility.sop
  + [eligibility_status] is eligible_for_manual_merge_packet, blocked_by_manager, blocked_by_shaliach, needs_revision, or needs_human_review
  + [manager_review_ref] is required
  + [shaliach_review_ref] is required
  + [generated_file_set] is required
  + [authority_boundary] is merge_eligibility_not_manual_merge_packet
  = must: never create a manual merge packet directly
  = must: never apply files to target workspace

& [ProofExpectations] is the minimum implementation proof for this design
  + [test_case] is Manager review record preserves not-apply boundary
  + [test_case] is Shaliach review record preserves not-Manager-acceptance boundary
  + [test_case] is merge eligibility combines accepted and clear into eligible_for_manual_merge_packet
  + [test_case] is Manager rejection blocks eligibility
  + [test_case] is Shaliach pause blocks eligibility
  + [test_case] is generated file refs outside run-local root fail validation

& [ImplementationOrder] is the safe next split
  + [slice_1] is add ManagerRunLocalOutputReview ShaliachRunLocalOutputReview and MergeEligibilitySummary records
  + [slice_2] is add validation helper for generated refs and eligibility decisions
  + [slice_3] is add explicit CLI writer for reviews and eligibility after tests
  + [slice_4] is only later connect eligible outputs to manual merge packet construction
